  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INTRO</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Excidio the Kaiju Simulator invites you to immerse yourself as a massive kaiju and lay waste to fully destructible physics-based environments at your leisure. Topple familiar landmarks and take on the military and other Kaiju that dare threaten you.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY AS A KAIJU</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras/3017d6fc7a59e729b74a453446abd1b1.avif?t=1771711107\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras_big/3017d6fc7a59e729b74a453446abd1b1.avif?t=1771711107 width=800 height=450 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself as one of three unique kaiju, Excidio, Golem or Raijin!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PHYSICS-BASED DESTRUCTION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras/80225fe030c778d9c732a764a9dc2d3e.poster.avif?t=1771711107\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras/80225fe030c778d9c732a764a9dc2d3e.webm?t=1771711107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras/80225fe030c778d9c732a764a9dc2d3e.mp4?t=1771711107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully physics-based realistic destruction. Walk through buildings only leaving rubble behind.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DESTROY 5 UNIQUE CITIES </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras/1c9f3f0a19c0afd889f50a6bf655493b.avif?t=1771711107\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras_big/1c9f3f0a19c0afd889f50a6bf655493b.avif?t=1771711107 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play on a variety of unique maps inspired by real locations!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TWO UNIQUE GAME MODES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ARCADE MODE - Upgrade your kaiju as you try and survive the onslaught of constant enemies! Can you get to the final wave?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SANDBOX MODE - Featuring a variety of customizable options for you to play as you please.  </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PHOTO MODES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a variety of photo modes and filters to capture screenshots and see the destruction from unique perspectives! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CROSSOVERS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dawn of the Monsters TM and ©2023 13AM Games, Megadon© 2023 13AM Games, Inc. All rights reserved. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terror of Hemasaurus Copyright 2024 Games By Loren.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Primatus Rex created by Dangerville.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Titanic Creations all rights reserved.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INTRO</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Excidio the Kaiju Simulator invites you to immerse yourself as a massive kaiju and lay waste to fully destructible physics-based environments at your leisure. Topple familiar landmarks and take on the military and other Kaiju that dare threaten you.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY AS A KAIJU</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras/3017d6fc7a59e729b74a453446abd1b1.avif?t=1771711107\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras_big/3017d6fc7a59e729b74a453446abd1b1.avif?t=1771711107 width=800 height=450 /></span>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself as one of three unique kaiju, Excidio, Golem or Raijin!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PHYSICS-BASED DESTRUCTION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras/80225fe030c778d9c732a764a9dc2d3e.poster.avif?t=1771711107\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras/80225fe030c778d9c732a764a9dc2d3e.webm?t=1771711107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras/80225fe030c778d9c732a764a9dc2d3e.mp4?t=1771711107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully physics-based realistic destruction. Walk through buildings only leaving rubble behind.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DESTROY 5 UNIQUE CITIES </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras/1c9f3f0a19c0afd889f50a6bf655493b.avif?t=1771711107\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594130/extras_big/1c9f3f0a19c0afd889f50a6bf655493b.avif?t=1771711107 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play on a variety of unique maps inspired by real locations!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TWO UNIQUE GAME MODES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ARCADE MODE - Upgrade your kaiju as you try and survive the onslaught of constant enemies! Can you get to the final wave?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >SANDBOX MODE - Featuring a variety of customizable options for you to play as you please.  </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PHOTO MODES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use a variety of photo modes and filters to capture screenshots and see the destruction from unique perspectives! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CROSSOVERS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dawn of the Monsters TM and ©2023 13AM Games, Megadon© 2023 13AM Games, Inc. All rights reserved. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Terror of Hemasaurus Copyright 2024 Games By Loren.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Primatus Rex created by Dangerville.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Titanic Creations all rights reserved.</p></li></ul>",
